COVID-19 Treatment Guidelines
National Institutes of Health

Key Recommendations:
- Mild COVID-19: Symptomatic treatment
- Moderate COVID-19: Consider antiviral therapy
- Severe COVID-19: Use corticosteroids + oxygen support

Antiviral Options:
- Nirmatrelvir/ritonavir (Paxlovid) for high-risk outpatients
- Remdesivir for hospitalized patients

Special Populations:
- Immunocompromised: Extended antiviral courses
- Pregnancy: Favipiravir not recommended
